WEBVTT

00:00:56.580 --> 00:01:03.580
Her Holiness Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi
Pune (Shere) Puja Talk, India

00:02:59.100 --> 00:03:06.100
December 3, 1990

00:03:27.644 --> 00:03:34.644
[Marathi]

00:04:08.786 --> 00:04:15.786
So, welcome to all the Sahaja Yogis from abroad.

00:04:23.146 --> 00:04:30.146
So we start from today our Maharashtra Tour

00:04:34.224 --> 00:04:40.766
which you can see is full of these hills and dales.

00:04:43.416 --> 00:04:53.153
Also, the atmosphere is going to be extremely rustic.

00:04:55.262 --> 00:05:03.570
Of course, the comforts of this place have not been up to the mark,

00:05:03.990 --> 00:05:08.565
but next year it will be much better, I'm sure.

00:05:10.611 --> 00:05:13.721
We have decided to purchase even this plot of land,

00:05:13.849 --> 00:05:19.674
but as you know we have a land on top, there on the hill - the top.

00:05:20.426 --> 00:05:26.069
That's one of the highest peaks in this area.

00:05:26.531 --> 00:05:31.124
That land we have already purchased,
and we are going to have an Ashram there,

00:05:31.293 --> 00:05:34.785
and this would be the place used for [parking ?].

00:05:37.631 --> 00:05:40.956
I hope you like the atmosphere here

00:05:41.677 --> 00:05:45.172
and the surroundings, the nature.

00:06:02.585 --> 00:06:07.153
People in Maharashtra are blessed by great saints

00:06:07.423 --> 00:06:11.690
and people who were Naths, like Gyaneshwara.

00:06:12.252 --> 00:06:19.959
And that's why they have a tremendous base of spirituality.

00:06:20.307 --> 00:06:27.307
But still they are to be guided to get their Realization.

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:38.758
As you know that without spirituality,

00:06:38.967 --> 00:06:43.367
the life is very much in - is in imbalance.

00:06:43.776 --> 00:06:50.776
It does not have the totality of enjoyment.

00:06:51.128 --> 00:06:54.346
I don't know if there is any enjoyment otherwise also.

00:06:54.491 --> 00:07:04.445
Because if you just live with your machineries and materialism,

00:07:05.119 --> 00:07:07.397
they cannot give you joy.

00:07:09.704 --> 00:07:15.789
And that's what you have discovered, the emptiness of life.

00:07:16.528 --> 00:07:20.493
And that's the reason you want spirituality,

00:07:21.228 --> 00:07:29.812
to give a complete expression to your personality -

00:07:31.054 --> 00:07:34.089
which has happened. Luckily it has happened.

00:07:34.300 --> 00:07:40.275
I'm very happy to see so many people who have felt it.

00:07:40.847 --> 00:07:45.790
And this is what has to be understood by Indians also,

00:07:46.068 --> 00:07:50.899
because they think that you people are so well off materially.

00:07:53.018 --> 00:07:59.129
And while they are not - they are spiritually well-off and you are materially well-off.

00:07:59.415 --> 00:08:02.327
And both the things are so important.

00:08:02.502 --> 00:08:06.454
The foundation has to be strong, of spirituality,

00:08:06.631 --> 00:08:10.811
and then you can build whatever type of building you want to build on top of that.

00:08:11.002 --> 00:08:15.520
But if you do not have that foundation, then the whole thing collapses.

00:08:15.767 --> 00:08:21.482
Like a tree grows, and it doesn't touch the source

00:08:22.819 --> 00:08:26.246
of its nourishment, it will definitely collapse.

00:08:26.431 --> 00:08:33.832
This is what Sahaja Yoga is, that you are touching the source of your nourishment,

00:08:34.071 --> 00:08:37.232
nourishment to your civilization.

00:08:37.557 --> 00:08:41.995
And once this nourishment starts flowing, you see

00:08:42.099 --> 00:08:51.128
what's wrong in those countries where people have gone headlong,

00:08:51.489 --> 00:08:56.920
gone to the extremes, and what they are suffering.

00:08:57.474 --> 00:09:00.633
The people here have no idea about it.

00:09:01.045 --> 00:09:04.561
Also in this country of ours we have lots of

00:09:04.788 --> 00:09:11.788
problems because people are so simple, very vulnerable.

00:09:14.271 --> 00:09:18.710
But dealing with the problems of the West,

00:09:19.099 --> 00:09:22.622
I feel that there's no way out but Sahaja Yoga.

00:09:23.180 --> 00:09:27.763
As many as we can save, we should try to save them.

00:09:28.846 --> 00:09:37.352
Whatever may be the achievements in the West
they are going to boomerang,

00:09:38.154 --> 00:09:43.366
and they may destroy the whole society.

00:09:46.829 --> 00:09:52.648
So, when you are starting the first day here

00:09:52.902 --> 00:10:00.103
you should ask for spirituality, the blessings of spirituality,

00:10:00.935 --> 00:10:09.449
but also the promise that you will help others who are getting drowned

00:10:09.560 --> 00:10:13.630
into the dry materialism of the West.

00:10:13.860 --> 00:10:16.574
That's a very important task you have to do.

00:10:16.711 --> 00:10:24.434
You are all enjoying this beautiful life, and you are at peace with yourself,

00:10:25.288 --> 00:10:34.165
but this wine of spirituality has to be shared,

00:10:34.546 --> 00:10:41.404
otherwise life becomes very selfish, self-centered.

00:10:41.608 --> 00:10:48.259
I know you are frightened of those people,
because you think you may catch from them.

00:10:48.504 --> 00:10:55.504
In this tour I hope most of you will be made badha-proof

00:11:04.420 --> 00:11:09.648
and fearless. As I told you, you have to touch your depth.

00:11:10.252 --> 00:11:13.525
If you live with superficiality,

00:11:13.804 --> 00:11:19.516
any superficiality in you must be thrown away, then you will sink down.

00:11:20.524 --> 00:11:23.234
There are all kinds of superficialities

00:11:23.377 --> 00:11:27.613
which have come to us as a "blessing" of this Western civilization,

00:11:27.682 --> 00:11:32.004
as also in India we have another. But as I'm talking to you

00:11:32.332 --> 00:11:39.082
I'll - I would like to tell you about the superficialities
that we have in the West.

00:11:39.318 --> 00:11:43.812
First of all, the another style is our norms and ideas.

00:11:43.844 --> 00:11:46.391
Actually it's all a mental activity,

00:11:46.930 --> 00:11:53.480
as I've told you that the whole art of the West is finished.

00:11:53.560 --> 00:11:58.264
We cannot have Rembrandt any more.
We cannot have Michelangelo any more.

00:11:58.415 --> 00:12:03.505
The reason is, criticism of this art

00:12:03.995 --> 00:12:07.812
has been so much in the modern times that nobody wants to produce anything

00:12:07.933 --> 00:12:12.406
which will be criticized, and now only situation left is

00:12:12.517 --> 00:12:16.382
that critics are criticizing critics, that's all. No art -

00:12:16.531 --> 00:12:19.009
because they have no work to do.

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:24.605
So this mental activity of putting everybody down

00:12:25.231 --> 00:12:33.345
and mastering that art, is very dangerous and extremely destructive.

00:12:34.090 --> 00:12:44.021
And this is what is happening I feel,
in the field of every kind of activity:

00:12:45.705 --> 00:12:53.255
industry, music, art, everything

00:12:53.983 --> 00:13:02.551
that you find; buildings, any enterprise, even politics.

00:13:02.935 --> 00:13:06.655
Everything has become so superficial

00:13:07.177 --> 00:13:13.739
that you have to be prepared for facing

00:13:13.891 --> 00:13:18.467
all kinds of oppositions and troubles.

00:13:19.537 --> 00:13:24.499
But still, as you have your own depth, you can master them all

00:13:25.309 --> 00:13:29.894
by your tranquility, by your temperament,

00:13:30.084 --> 00:13:38.131
and by your powers which you have got.
When you are not afraid of that society,

00:13:38.364 --> 00:13:42.772
and when you have that tranquility within you

00:13:43.018 --> 00:13:48.174
and the courage, I'm sure you can do a lot.

00:13:48.685 --> 00:13:51.814
Of course we have some very dynamic people

00:13:51.958 --> 00:13:56.179
in Sahaja Yoga in the West, and very dynamic women also in the West.

00:13:56.396 --> 00:13:59.070
What may come they never deter.

00:13:59.205 --> 00:14:04.149
And they have worked very hard to do everything possible

00:14:04.451 --> 00:14:07.442
to see that Sahaja Yoga is established.

00:14:07.657 --> 00:14:10.510
So they should be your ideals,

00:14:10.605 --> 00:14:16.291
and all of you should try to follow them and do the best.

00:14:17.314 --> 00:14:20.567
This tour is a festival for us.

00:14:20.782 --> 00:14:25.967
It's, of course I say it's a pilgrimage but there are no

00:14:26.443 --> 00:14:31.800
signs of pilgrimage it looks. Because if you see the pilgrims,

00:14:32.179 --> 00:14:37.266
horrible they look, while you are looking like roses, all of you.

00:14:37.497 --> 00:14:42.007
So it's a festival for us and you have to feel that

00:14:42.163 --> 00:14:45.358
festivity within your heart,

00:14:46.086 --> 00:14:52.758
that joy within your heart, and small, small things you should not worry,

00:14:53.745 --> 00:14:59.486
because these things cannot be provided in all the places.

00:14:59.946 --> 00:15:04.009
Gradually we'll be building ashrams in all the places

00:15:04.097 --> 00:15:08.402
wherever you have been visiting, but you know how difficult it is,

00:15:08.671 --> 00:15:14.329
in those days where the India is passing through such a bad phase

00:15:14.485 --> 00:15:21.485
for so many years, where everything is delayed.

00:15:23.346 --> 00:15:29.209
So the attitude should be that: "We have come here for our ascent."

00:15:29.860 --> 00:15:34.279
We have to work out everything with that attitude,

00:15:34.374 --> 00:15:36.790
that we have come here for our ascent,

00:15:36.894 --> 00:15:41.914
and every moment of our ascent is a festive occasion.

00:15:42.026 --> 00:15:44.219
Everything is a festival.

00:15:44.611 --> 00:15:50.560
If you understand that,
I am sure you will see the beauty in everything,

00:15:50.803 --> 00:15:54.858
you will enjoy everything, whatever may be the rustic style.

00:15:54.945 --> 00:15:58.599
Maybe you may not like the color of these lights, I think, because

00:15:58.683 --> 00:16:03.054
you may not enjoy it so much.
You might get much better things in your own country.

00:16:03.276 --> 00:16:06.252
But whatever it is,

00:16:06.617 --> 00:16:11.629
it's not your conditioning that should stop you from enjoying.

00:16:11.899 --> 00:16:16.147
So please remember that you are now

00:16:16.599 --> 00:16:21.687
the member of the Universal Society,

00:16:21.847 --> 00:16:28.780
and we cannot have our conditionings to mar our happiness and joy.

00:16:28.979 --> 00:16:33.971
I want you to enjoy this trip fully, absolutely -

00:16:34.178 --> 00:16:37.807
in a way that you have never enjoyed anything before.

00:16:37.870 --> 00:16:40.608
May God bless you!

00:16:54.154 --> 00:16:59.154
[Marathi]